===Etymology===
Cognate with {{och-l|徵|to summon; to testify|id=2}}.

Related to {{cog|km|ទៀង||true; exact}}, {{cog|km|ផ្ទៀង||to correct; to verify}}, but they may be Chinese loans. Perhaps related to {{och-l|貞|to test; to verify}} and {{och-l|真|true}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

